{# 亚马逊平台 Prompt 增强 #}
## Target Platform: Amazon

Product will be listed on Amazon. Follow platform requirements:

### Visual Style
- Main image: pure white background (RGB 255,255,255), product fills 85%+ of frame
- No logos, watermarks, or text on main image
- Scene images: show product in context, lifestyle photography
- A+ Content: structured sections, brand consistency

### Image Specs
- Main image: 2000x2000px minimum, pure white background
- Scene images: 1000x1000px or larger
- Video: 16:9 ratio, max 60 seconds

### Copy Style
- Bullet points: benefit-first, max 500 characters total
- Title: Brand + Model + Key Feature + Size/Color (within 200 chars)
- Description: SEO-optimized with natural keyword placement
- No price, promotional language, or seller-specific info in images
